Re: Missed (opportunity)
by Hyperworm » Sat 01.08.2011 11:45 am 100PercentWeasel wrote:How would one express missing another person? I know japanese don't 'miss' each other so how do they express it?From what I've seen, reading Japanese material, the closest equivalent is 会いたい・会いたかった.
